# Biomedical / experimental data
# Do not upload raw or sensitive participant data.
# ============================================================

data/raw/
data/interim/
data/processed/
data/external/
data/private/
data/consents/
data/participants/
data/identifiable/
data/**/raw/
data/**/private/
data/**/consents/

